[normal] of it. It is beyond your remit I think.
[normal]Chair:[bold] But it is not beyond our intellectual capabilities. Some of us may appear to be piecemeal but still have a master plan in mind. Others of us botch along depending on what the political winds are and what expedience can deliver for us. I am not sure in which camp I or my 
[normal]Committee
